<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa thla tang, him tein ka dor zungzal, Zan tlai in thlichia hrang
 chin hmanhsehlaw, Ka zumh ko rih lai, A kut in a ka hruai, A ka tlanh
 cang i a fa ka si cang.

[C1]
   A thla tangah ka um zungzal, Amah a kan dawtnak in zeihmanh nih a ka
   then kho lai lo, A thla tangah ka him ko.

[V2]
 A thla tang cu ngaihchiami dornak a si, Bawipa sin ah lung daih
 dinhnak a um, Vawlei ah kei ca damnak si a um lo, Khikhin lung daih le
 hnangamnak ka hmu.

[C2]
   A thla tangah ka um zungzal, Amah a kan dawtnak in zeihmanh nih a ka
   then kho lai lo, A thla tangah ka him ko.

[V3]
 Bawipa thla tang a sung bik lunglawmhnak ah, Vawlei harnak a dongh
 tiang ka um lai, A ka huhphenh ca sual nih a ka tei lo, Bawi Jesuh
 hngatchan in ka him zungzal.

[C3]
   A thla tangah ka um zungzal, Amah a kan dawtnak in zeihmanh nih a ka
   then kho lai lo, A thla tangah ka him ko.</lyrics>
<key>Db</key>
<title>A THLA TANGAH CH63</title>
<hymn_number>63</hymn_number>
</song>